name: Igreja Universal do Reino das NFT
description:
.
.
.
Our Tezo, who art in Kukai,
globalised be thy node;
thy baker come;
thy interaction be done;
on earth as it is in Metaverse.
Give us this day our daily Mint.
And forgive us our flops,
as we collect our mate’s NFTs

And lead us not into shilling;
but deliver us from gas.
For thine is the blockchain,
the spaces and the community ,
for ever and ever.
GM.

.
.
.
ANGEL NUMBER 999
